WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.667
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:02.667 --> 00:00:03.943
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.943 --> 00:00:06.000
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.399
Well, I just want to thank every single one of you again.

00:00:10.399 --> 00:00:10.949
Thank you for coming.

00:00:10.949 --> 00:00:14.259
Every single time we do a video, you come out and you pray.

00:00:14.259 --> 00:00:15.462
You take things seriously.

00:00:16.285 --> 00:00:17.952
This is where I've been.

00:00:17.952 --> 00:00:25.189
I told the Lord, I said, "I don't want to be where I'm at today this way tomorrow.

00:00:25.189 --> 00:00:29.840
I'm tired of being just the status quo.

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:31.580
I'm tired of the status quo.

00:00:31.580 --> 00:00:34.423
I'm tired of Christianity as usual.

00:00:34.423 --> 00:00:36.848
I'm ready for Christianity unusual.

00:00:37.984 --> 00:00:43.754
" This is why when you get fed up being the way you are, that's when you'll start to see change.

00:00:43.754 --> 00:00:44.137
I want change.

00:00:44.137 --> 00:00:47.982
Diana and I, Braden, Megan, all of us.

00:00:47.982 --> 00:00:49.369
I want change in my daughter.

00:00:49.369 --> 00:00:51.050
I want change in my family.

00:00:51.050 --> 00:00:55.510
I want change, expecting God to do something big in your life.

00:00:55.510 --> 00:00:59.312
And I said, "Lord, I want the revival.

00:00:59.312 --> 00:01:05.320
I want healings, demonstrations, and manifestations of your glory in these last days.

00:01:05.320 --> 00:01:07.250
You said we would walk in this.

00:01:07.500 --> 00:01:09.700
Where's the kink in the hose?

00:01:11.893 --> 00:01:17.230
" And the Bible says, "If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will.

00:01:17.230 --> 00:01:29.291
" But it's about remaining in this word and getting this word's foundation in your life, the love walk, going back to 1 Corinthians 13 and meditating on what He said.

00:01:29.566 --> 00:01:59.180
Getting that word, the love, because the glory of what He said, Brandon—the glory of those big silos of that honey glow—was connected to love, getting a love foundation in your life from 1 Corinthians 13, meditating on that, and getting that word of what the Bible says about love taking no account of a suffered wrong when people do you wrong and all these things, but also believing God that He's going to do it.

00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:05.770
Having an expectation for manifestations, because expectation brings the manifestation.

00:02:05.770 --> 00:02:13.831
I believe that God is going to show up in this service tomorrow for your churches, or for wherever you have a church or prayer group.

00:02:13.831 --> 00:02:19.343
I expect for us to get something radical from the Holy Spirit today.

00:02:19.343 --> 00:02:30.727
I do not want to go away and have another lukewarm service that everybody kind of feels was okay, whatever, bypassing another week.

00:02:30.727 --> 00:02:36.098
I know from glory to glory He's changing me.

00:02:36.098 --> 00:02:38.187
I want that so bad.

00:02:38.187 --> 00:02:47.314
The only thing that's ever going to change you is having a foundation of this word down inside of your heart, changing you from the inside out.

00:02:47.314 --> 00:02:48.571
That's the only thing.

00:02:48.571 --> 00:02:51.805
And that's what Brother Hagin—he drove it home.

00:02:51.805 --> 00:02:56.080
That's all he ever talked about: "Faith cometh by hearing, hearing by the word of God," you know.

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:56.920
And R.

00:02:56.920 --> 00:02:57.900
W.

00:02:57.900 --> 00:03:00.040
Schambach, all the greats.

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:02.512
I said, "My goodness, Lord, help me.

00:03:02.512 --> 00:03:05.889
If I'm a closer, I don't want to let these guys down.

00:03:05.889 --> 00:03:08.983
I don't want to let you down.

00:03:18.898 --> 00:03:19.049
I want to finish strong.

00:03:19.049 --> 00:03:26.067
Lord, let us do something big for you because the word is working mightily in me.

00:03:31.059 --> 00:03:31.946
The word is working mightily in me.

00:03:31.946 --> 00:03:33.680
Do you believe it?

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.109
Do you believe it?

00:03:35.109 --> 00:03:53.804
" But then He said to me when I was driving around today, He said, "Brandon, I want you to start to believe for manifestations of angelic encounters—not flaky stuff, but truly changing you from the inside out—the word, believing for that.

00:03:53.804 --> 00:04:02.452
But not only that, believing for demonstrations of the Holy Spirit, manifestations of the Holy Spirit, and angelic visitations in your services every day, Lord, by love.

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:11.820
" I get this love like He said, love from 1 Corinthians 13.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:21.626
Get in that love.

00:04:21.626 --> 00:04:38.737
Okay, so if I'm walking in love, and you are love, and you're inside of me, and I'm inside with you, Lord, and we take this communion every day, and we're expecting for you to show up in the mall, showing up in these circumstances.

00:04:38.737 --> 00:04:52.453
There was a guy, when I had all these things going on with our house, I told you the guy hit our septic, and it was like thousands of dollars to get this septic fixed.

00:04:52.453 --> 00:05:01.360
But when he was here, my first reaction was just to lose it, because he just did all this, right?

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:08.880
And he wasn't going to fix it because I didn't tell him where the septic was.

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:13.340
So it was, you know, and he said, "I'll go in half.

00:05:13.340 --> 00:05:16.114
" But the Holy Spirit said, "Walk in love.

00:05:16.114 --> 00:05:16.960
Walk in love.

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:17.599
Walk in love.

00:05:17.599 --> 00:05:19.759
Don't lose it on this man.

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:23.169
There's more to this than what meets the eye.

00:05:26.090 --> 00:05:30.707
" And so, to make a long story short, another guy came, and he was a Hispanic man, and the Lord said to me, "He does not know me.

00:05:30.707 --> 00:05:35.466
" Witness to him, impart love into him, and talk to him about the word.

00:05:35.466 --> 00:05:40.920
You could feel instantaneously the devil inside of him starts talking out.

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:43.234
"Are you smoking dope?

00:05:43.234 --> 00:05:45.600
Are you doing this stuff?

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:50.440
" because you're talking about the Holy Ghost.

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:54.240
You're talking about the end times, "Jesus is coming.

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:56.270
The end times are here.

00:05:56.270 --> 00:06:00.230
" I'm just bold about my faith, folks.

00:06:00.230 --> 00:06:05.027
I'm not going to ever just back down.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:10.159
And if the Holy Spirit comes on me, you're going to see a radical evangelist right there.

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:12.080
And that's what I do.

00:06:30.790 --> 00:06:31.000
And so I start telling him about the Antichrist and about earthquakes.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:32.280
This is what's coming.

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:36.619
Oregon is fixing to have a major earthquake.

00:06:36.619 --> 00:06:40.595
This is stuff because I know God puts these signs.

00:06:40.595 --> 00:06:42.436
Signs will follow them that believe.

00:06:42.436 --> 00:06:45.668
Signs will follow them that believe; He said they would.

00:07:01.150 --> 00:07:01.420
And God gives us these things to be a light in the darkness to this world, not to be flaky.

00:07:01.420 --> 00:07:03.039
What makes us stand out?

00:07:03.039 --> 00:07:04.182
It's the signs.

00:07:04.182 --> 00:07:05.729
It's the wonders.

00:07:05.729 --> 00:07:20.829
It's whenever we touch somebody, and they are lost as a goose in the fog, and you lay hands on them, and the power of God sets them free, and they go from glory to glory.

00:07:20.829 --> 00:07:22.140
There was something to that.

00:07:22.140 --> 00:07:39.088
It's not just watered-down, lukewarm religion that you're getting from stale preachers behind the pulpit, but you're teaching people that Jesus Christ is coming and they need to repent because if they don't, they're going to hell.

00:07:42.710 --> 00:07:42.941
He came to set the captives free.

00:07:42.941 --> 00:07:57.333
He told us to do the Great Commission: to go into all the world, lay hands on the sick, and they would recover, cast out devils, raise the dead, do all the things that He said we could do.

00:07:57.333 --> 00:07:59.759
Why aren't we seeing it?

00:08:04.840 --> 00:08:05.029
Because we're not believing it.

00:08:05.029 --> 00:08:06.880
I want to be a believing believer.

00:08:07.307 --> 00:08:13.319
And when I saw that man, the Lord told me, "If he dies tonight, Brandon, he's going to hell.

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:15.955
" I had compassion inside of me.

00:08:15.955 --> 00:08:29.805
I wanted to—it would look flaky—but bend down on my knees right then and grab his ankle and say, "If you die tonight, sir, the Lord told me you're going to hell.

00:08:29.805 --> 00:08:33.565
I don't know what it is with you, but God's calling you.

00:08:33.565 --> 00:08:36.947
God's calling you.

00:08:36.947 --> 00:08:39.760
God's calling your son that's standing next to you.

00:08:40.060 --> 00:08:46.107
" And I feel to intercede and just weep on behalf of your soul because you don't realize how close you are to stepping over.

00:08:46.107 --> 00:08:52.360
I don't know what it was about that man, but he came to my house, and I figured he's here for a reason.

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:53.387
It's not a coincidence.

00:08:53.387 --> 00:08:55.547
"Yeah, you messed up my septic.

00:08:55.547 --> 00:09:07.499
Yeah, you did all this stuff, and I'm showing you love because my flesh wants to just be really ugly right now.

00:09:07.499 --> 00:09:09.880
What do you do for a living, sir?

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:10.950
" "I'm a preacher.

00:09:10.950 --> 00:09:13.520
" "I could be a real jerk right now.

00:09:13.520 --> 00:09:21.977
I really could because of what you did, but I'm going to show you love, and I'm going to pay for it.

00:09:21.977 --> 00:09:24.453
I'm going to pay for it.

00:09:37.531 --> 00:09:37.829
It doesn't cost you anything.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:39.360
It was an accident.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:53.074
" But you have the opportunity right then to show the love of God to somebody, and you can totally lose it because thousands of dollars is a lot, or you can love on somebody because they made a mistake.

00:09:53.074 --> 00:10:02.786
Yeah, it was a costly one, but my point is that's the love that He's talking about in 1 Corinthians 13 right now.

00:10:02.786 --> 00:10:12.569
Not all things are always easy, especially when you're dealing with the world and they mess up your yard and they do all the things that they do.

00:10:12.569 --> 00:10:13.520
And you know what?

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:17.200
The one guy came back and made it all right.

00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:22.470
He went out and cleaned up the stuff, and he apologized because it was bad.

00:10:33.317 --> 00:10:34.593
I'm just telling y'all, it was bad.

00:10:34.593 --> 00:10:37.137
A lot of things.

00:10:37.137 --> 00:10:39.146
My house is leaking water clear into my bedroom.

00:10:39.146 --> 00:10:41.223
There's a lot going on this last week.

00:10:41.223 --> 00:10:43.520
Then we made the video last week.

00:10:43.520 --> 00:10:47.063
Wednesday evening, we got home from church, did all that, got so excited.

00:10:47.063 --> 00:10:48.503
Thursday morning, we woke up.

00:10:48.503 --> 00:10:53.159
We're going to make another video for you all, and Braden's computer has completely crashed.

00:10:57.095 --> 00:10:57.920
All of the software, all of it completely gone, wiped out.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.891
It's like we got hacked in the middle of the night.

00:11:00.891 --> 00:11:02.699
Literally, the computer won't start, won't do anything.

00:11:06.423 --> 00:11:06.845
And he goes, 'Daddy, something bad has happened to the computer that we got blessed with.

00:11:06.845 --> 00:11:11.600
It's not working at all.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:14.382
' And I said, 'What happened?

00:11:14.382 --> 00:11:16.846
' He goes, 'It won't even boot up.

00:11:16.846 --> 00:11:17.874
There's nothing.

00:11:21.473 --> 00:11:21.959
It won't even do anything.

00:11:21.959 --> 00:11:24.720
' It was completely frozen.

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:29.235
Everything about this after we made that video about the energy and everything.

00:11:29.235 --> 00:11:32.509
So, I figured we got hacked.

00:11:32.509 --> 00:11:36.720
Something happened in the middle of the night.

00:11:40.816 --> 00:11:41.072
I still don't know what happened.

00:11:41.072 --> 00:11:44.187
So, he had to reboot it back up.

00:11:44.187 --> 00:11:46.794
He's watching YouTube videos.

00:11:48.691 --> 00:11:56.330
All these little pricks because I know I'm on the right road and I'm going somewhere with this.

00:12:01.530 --> 00:12:14.777
You know you're on the right road when you're getting these little pricks because the enemy is ticked off because I'm putting a kink in his hose and he doesn't like it because I'm teaching a lot of you.

00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:23.260
You know how many people email every day, 'You're teaching me to pray.

00:12:23.260 --> 00:12:25.310
You're teaching me how to live by faith.

00:12:45.188 --> 00:12:45.519
I was suicidal.

00:12:45.519 --> 00:12:47.120
My marriage has been restored.

00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:51.160
' How many people have gotten their lives changed by watching these videos?

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:52.030
I'm humbled.

00:12:52.030 --> 00:12:57.556
So many people said, 'I never knew how to pray in the Holy Ghost and baptism.

00:12:57.556 --> 00:13:06.617
I got filled with the Holy Ghost and fire watching these videos and I pray with you every single day.

00:13:06.617 --> 00:13:11.840
' How many people said, 'I was lukewarm and you turned me around?

00:13:11.840 --> 00:13:16.550
I watch you instead of pastors now because I get more out of your sermons.

00:13:16.550 --> 00:13:20.756
' I said, 'My God, what an honor that you'd come to listen to me.

00:13:20.756 --> 00:13:34.213
' But after you get all these little pricks and things, and Braden finally, it was the grace of God watching a YouTube video that we were able to—because he said, 'Daddy, we're going to have to buy a new computer.

00:13:47.792 --> 00:13:47.984
This computer's gone.

00:13:47.984 --> 00:13:51.120
' And watching a YouTube video, he fixed it.

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:52.133
Thank God.

00:13:52.133 --> 00:13:54.820
Took him all day long Thursday.

00:13:54.820 --> 00:13:57.327
All day long, we didn't have it.

00:13:57.327 --> 00:14:02.030
And I told him, I said, 'Whatever happens happens, buddy.

00:14:02.030 --> 00:14:03.380
We'll make it work.

00:14:03.380 --> 00:14:11.246
' Whenever the enemy comes in and he tries to test you to see if he's getting to you by how you react.

00:14:11.246 --> 00:14:25.240
How are you reacting to the septic tank getting run over, the water line, and the water flooding my bathroom and ruining it, and I had to go and fix all that, the boards falling down from the storm?

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:27.554
All these little things.

00:14:28.017 --> 00:14:34.490
The enemy tried to get you all in your thoughts, but it all goes back to 1 Corinthians 13.

00:14:34.490 --> 00:14:36.400
Will you walk in love?

00:14:36.400 --> 00:14:39.848
Will you allow your fruit to shine to men?

00:14:57.491 --> 00:14:59.434
And whenever the devil's trying to get your joy with all these little things and it all adds up, like I said, thousands, and my flesh, like I said, I was—wow.

00:14:59.434 --> 00:15:00.170
Okay.

00:15:00.170 --> 00:15:07.160
So, whenever all that's coming on you and all that's going on and you have the opportunity to walk in love, right?

00:15:07.160 --> 00:15:08.720
Walk in love.

00:15:08.720 --> 00:15:11.440
The Bible says, 'Take no thought, saying.

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:13.600
' Take no thought, saying.

00:15:13.600 --> 00:15:14.320
Why?

00:15:21.765 --> 00:15:22.056
Because out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:15:27.337 --> 00:15:27.748
And the devil cannot read your thoughts.

00:15:29.404 --> 00:15:30.879
The devil can't go around looking, 'Am I getting to him?

00:15:30.879 --> 00:15:38.228
' So the only way he can know if he's getting to you is by how you're responding on the outside in the natural.

00:15:38.228 --> 00:15:40.760
Because the devil's a flesh devil.

00:15:51.840 --> 00:15:52.048
He doesn't get anything by the spirit of God.

00:15:53.130 --> 00:15:54.130
He has to move by the flesh.

00:15:54.130 --> 00:15:55.220
And he's not omnipresent.

00:15:55.220 --> 00:15:57.200
He is either with you or whatever.

00:15:57.200 --> 00:15:59.909
He's not like the Holy Spirit, right?

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:09.140
So, his demons are looking to go back and report to him, 'This worked and this didn't work.

00:16:09.140 --> 00:16:15.609
' But when you show the love of God, you pass the test.

00:16:15.609 --> 00:16:18.913
That's what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:16:31.420 --> 00:16:32.070
When you get cut off on the road, when you do these things and people treat you badly at the restaurant—you might have a bad server at the restaurant.

00:16:32.070 --> 00:16:40.310
She might give you bad service and you show love and say, 'I'll give her a good tip anyway.

00:16:40.310 --> 00:16:41.413
She doesn't deserve it.

00:16:41.413 --> 00:16:48.418
' And you might want to just tell her boss, 'She's the most lousy server I've ever had.

00:16:48.418 --> 00:16:50.686
She didn't get my drinks refilled.

00:16:50.686 --> 00:16:55.690
She didn't give me good service the whole time.

00:16:55.690 --> 00:17:15.085
I'm telling you what, I want to let this girl have a piece of my mind,' you know, but you go and you say, 'Honey, I know this may not be your calling, but I'm going to bless you anyway and show you love,' you know, 20 bucks or whatever.

00:17:15.085 --> 00:17:23.213
I don't know, that's a big tip, I'm just saying you give them a big tip.

00:17:23.213 --> 00:17:29.100
They may say, 'Hey, I can't believe how I treated you' or whatever.

00:17:29.100 --> 00:17:45.006
I don't know, I just try to show God's love until the point of where it's painful to my flesh because there's something more about it in the glory, is what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:17:45.006 --> 00:17:46.464
Where is the glory?

00:17:46.464 --> 00:17:49.165
Where's the outpouring of the spirit of God?

00:17:49.165 --> 00:17:51.675
Like we've never seen it before.

00:18:02.933 --> 00:18:03.119
The Lord told me, he said, 'Brandon, Jesus did not do any mighty works until somebody put a demand on it.

00:18:03.119 --> 00:18:06.080
' Look at what he did with the water turning into wine.

00:18:06.080 --> 00:18:09.360
Mary put a demand on that gift inside of him.

00:18:09.360 --> 00:18:10.622
But it wasn't time yet.

00:18:10.622 --> 00:18:17.626
30 years, nothing, and then somebody put a demand on it and caused that gift to flourish.

00:18:24.674 --> 00:18:25.091
And that's why I feel like a lot of times, maybe that's where we're at.

00:18:25.091 --> 00:18:27.627
Maybe it wasn't season yet.

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:36.384
But the Lord said it's time to put a demand on what is rightfully ours.

00:18:36.384 --> 00:18:40.100
When I was driving around today, he said it's time to put a demand on it.

00:18:40.100 --> 00:18:46.880
It's time for you to expect, because I was driving under a bridge.

00:18:53.234 --> 00:18:53.509
I can't even tell you where I was.

00:19:01.451 --> 00:19:01.794
I was on Memorial Drive in Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:19:08.410 --> 00:19:14.196
And I was going under the bridge because I was looking at the Range Rovers, I was looking at the Cadillac dealership, I was believing big.

00:19:20.133 --> 00:19:20.307
Looking at those cars and going, 'Look at those cars.

00:19:20.731 --> 00:19:23.783
That's the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:33.420
Look at those brand new Escalades, look at those brand new Range Rovers, look at those brand new cars.

00:19:33.420 --> 00:19:35.991
Look at what the world has.

00:19:35.991 --> 00:19:40.800
' And yes, they have it, but greater is he that is in me.

00:19:40.800 --> 00:19:41.520
Yes.

00:19:41.520 --> 00:19:48.469
He said he would provide, the wealth of the sinners is laid up for the righteous.

00:19:57.029 --> 00:19:57.514
I believe it.

00:20:10.960 --> 00:20:11.280
It's a wealth transfer time.

00:20:11.280 --> 00:20:13.710
Some people don't want to agree with me on that.

00:20:13.710 --> 00:20:17.239
That's fine, stay where you are, but don't criticize me for believing big.

00:20:17.439 --> 00:20:32.984
I was driving underneath the bridge there, and the Lord started talking to me about the angels, and he said, 'Brandon, remember I told you as you're passing under this bridge to believe for angelic visitation in these services?

00:20:50.107 --> 00:20:50.753
Believe for the angels to work with you to bring the body parts.

00:20:50.753 --> 00:21:06.107
' I told you when we got in prayer, if an octopus can get a new limb and grow back new limbs, if a crab can do it and they're sea-dwelling animals, how much more are you able to believe for a new arm or a new leg or new eyes?

00:21:06.107 --> 00:21:10.049
If they can grow back stuff, why can't we?

00:21:13.824 --> 00:21:14.376
We're created in his image.

00:21:14.376 --> 00:21:18.519
We're created to be the head over all these things.

00:21:18.519 --> 00:21:21.480
He said to take dominion and authority over these animals.

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:25.760
How much more do we have the ability to grow back something?

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:26.720
'Well, I don't believe that.

00:21:26.720 --> 00:21:27.749
We've never seen it.

00:21:27.749 --> 00:21:31.070
' It's time to believe for the impossible.

00:21:31.070 --> 00:21:32.845
It's time to believe.

00:21:32.845 --> 00:21:33.977
God forbid.

